    title: "11 Scientific Reasons That Extraterrestrial Life Almost Certainly Exists",
    excerpt: "The numbers are staggering. The chemistry is universal. Life on Earth has survived conditions that should have been impossible. Here are the eleven strongest scientific arguments that we are not alone.",
    category: "alien-theories",
