    title: "7 Declassified Government Documents That Prove UFOs Were Studied For Decades",
    excerpt: "Governments insist they never took UFOs seriously. Declassified documents from the US, UK, Canada, and France tell a very different story — one that spans decades and involves the highest levels of intelligence agencies.",
