    slug: "roswell-incident-new-evidence-75-years",
    title: "The Roswell Incident: What New Evidence Reveals After More Than 75 Years",
    excerpt: "Was it a weather balloon? A classified military project? Something else entirely? After 75 years, new documents, new testimonies, and new analysis have changed what we know about the most famous UFO incident in history.",
    category: "ufo-sightings",
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516339901601-2e1b62dc0c45?w=1200&q=80",
