    title: "What Happens When You Report A UFO Sighting In Canada — And Why Most People Don't",
    excerpt: "Canada has had an official mechanism for reporting UFO sightings since the 1960s. Here is how the system actually works, what happens to your report, and why thousands of Canadians who see something never say anything.",
    category: "canadian-encounters",
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?w=1200&q=80",
