    title: "What The Pentagon's Official UFO Office Has Actually Confirmed",
    excerpt: "The All-domain Anomaly Resolution Office was created specifically to investigate UAPs. Here is everything AARO has officially confirmed, what it has been denied access to, and what its reports quietly reveal.",
    category: "government-secrets",
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1444703686981-a3abbc4d4fe3?w=1200&q=80",
