    title: "What SETI Researchers Found In Their Latest Deep Space Survey — And Why It Matters",
    excerpt: "The Breakthrough Listen initiative has completed the largest SETI survey in history. Here is what was found, what wasn't, and why the silence is itself a scientifically significant finding.",
    category: "space-nasa",
