    title: "What Happens To Human Society The Day We Confirm Alien Life Exists",
    excerpt: "Scientists have modelled it. Governments have quietly prepared for it. Philosophers and theologians have written about it for decades. Here is the serious, evidence-based answer to what actually happens to humanity the day the news breaks.",
